text_logic_form: The triangle $XYZ$ is a right triangle.
The length of the line $XY$ is equal to the hypotenuse of the right triangle $XYZ$.
The length of the line $YP$ is equal to the length of the line $YZ$.
The measure of angle $PYZ$ is $26$ degrees.
